text: Henry Jennings (9 April 1849 - 6 June 1925) was an Australian cricketer. He played one first-class cricket match for Victoria in 1873. ==See also== * List of Victoria first-class cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1849 births Category:1925 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:Victoria cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Launceston, Tasmania
